parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Premature Wear of Front Brake Rotors and Pads
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature wear of front brake rotors and pads can lead to reduced braking performance, increased stopping distances, and potentially cause accidents.
symptoms: grinding or screeching noise when applying brakes
frequent need to replace brake pads and rotors.
